import React from 'react'
import { Col, Container, Jumbotron, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'
import Layout from '../../components/Layout/Layout'

function Home() {
    return (
        <Layout>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col md={2}>sidebar</Col>
                    <Col md={10}>sidebar</Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        </Layout>
    )
}

export default Home
